snippet.title: PALIKAT - SG-1000 Homebrew Gameplay
snippet.description:
A homebrew Tetris clone made for the SC-3000 home computer, helmha also converted the game for the SG-1000.

Palikat developed by helmha
Link: https://www.smspower.org/Homebrew/Palikat-SG

RetroArch Core: SMS Plus GX
